    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-07-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-07-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="377" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d377">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-07-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20,
                                1895</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mora matter awaiting final action council of state. Important to settle
                            currency question before it acts. Government perfectly able to make gold
                            payment.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Taylor.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
